{
  "name": "RPlog_A_Reunion",
  "title": "A Reunion",
  "summary": "In the lobby of the Imperial Embassy, the regal Venus Dekan DarkStar -- now Prime Minister of the Caspian Democratic Union, but once the Empress whose life the spymaster Joir was sworn to protect -- arrives announcing herself as Lady DarkStar to see the Chief Diplomatic Officer Chantinelle. Joir, stirred by a long-buried memory, recognizes her and approaches with stiff formality that gives way to genuine, guarded warmth. When the embassy informs Venus that Thistleborn is unavailable for hours, she instead accepts Joir's veiled invitation to a private visit and leads him to her own minimalist office in the People's Hall. There, free of bodyguards and pretense, the two old companions finally let the years of repressed feeling surface: Venus weeps at the sight of the man who once guarded her night and day and even betrayed his Emperor to keep her safe, and Joir, addressing her as 'Empress,' embraces her with uncharacteristic tenderness as both surrender to the bond they have long shared.",
